OL,3,CUnibet operator fined #10 million for
OL,4,Csocial responsibility failures
OL,6,FPlatinum Gaming, the operator of
OL,7,FUnibet and uk.bingo.com, has been
OL,8,Ffined #10 million for anti-money
OL,9,Flaundering (AML) and social
OL,10,Fresponsibility failings, the Gambling
OL,11,FCommission has said.
OL,13,FIt is the second round of enforcement
OL,14,Faction for Platinum Gaming after it
OL,15,Fwas fined #2.9 million in 2023.
OL,17,FThe failures this time round included
OL,18,Fallowing a player to lose #5,000 in 24
OL,19,Fhours of registration and go on to
OL,20,Flose more than #16,000 in less than
OL,21,Fthree months.
