OL,6,FThe operator also failed to interact
OL,7,Fwith a customer who lost more than
OL,8,F#31,000 within nine months and hit
OL,9,Ftheir monthly loss limit on six
OL,10,Foccasions.
OL,12,FAnother example saw the company fail
OL,13,Fto interact with a customer who
OL,14,Fexceeded their #2,500 loss limit
OL,15,Fwithin 16 minutes of registering their
OL,16,Faccount as potentially being at risk
OL,17,Fof harm.
