OL,3,CUnibet operator fined #10 million for
OL,4,Csocial responsibility failures
OL,6,FThe Gambling Commission's director of
OL,7,Fenforcement, John Pierce, said: "While
OL,8,Findustry-wide progress has been made
OL,9,Fin reducing unchecked high spending,
OL,10,Fthe failings at Platinum Gaming are
OL,11,Fparticularly disappointing.
OL,13,F"The case revealed serious
OL,14,Fshortcomings in customer interaction
OL,15,Fsystems, including failures to
OL,16,Fidentify and act on clear markers of
OL,17,Fharm.
