OL,4,Csocial responsibility failures
OL,6,F"These included consumers losing
OL,7,Fthousands within hours or days of
OL,8,Fregistration, repeatedly breaching
OL,9,Floss limits, and exhibiting patterns
OL,10,Fof binge and high-velocity gambling
OL,11,Fwithout appropriate intervention."
OL,13,FHe added: "Senior leaders must take
OL,14,Fownership of compliance outcomes and
OL,15,Fensure lessons are embedded across the
OL,16,Forganisation, supported by structured
OL,17,Freporting and board level oversight `
OL,18,Fand further regulatory activity will
OL,19,Fremain a possibility."
